{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act17side_level_act17side_st02","storyGroup":"act17side","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"act17side_level_act17side_01_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"SN-ST-2","storyName":"海滨小道","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"蒂亚戈试图说服乔迪离开，借此机会，蒂亚戈告知了乔迪关于格兰法洛的一切。面对漆黑的大海，人们似乎无路可去。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act17side/level_act17side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act17side_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["蒂亚戈","乔迪","寡言的教徒","圣徒卡门","凯尔希","Alty","Dan","Aya","歌蕾蒂娅","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨？","幽灵鲨","慌张的镇民","深海教徒A","深海教徒B"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_snowconutryinside","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"$darkness02_loop","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","fadetime":"1","id":8},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.7","id":9},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"乔迪！","id":12,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"啊......蒂亚戈叔叔......怎么了吗？","id":14,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......你......快收拾东西，准备离开这里。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"呃、怎、怎么了？我们要去哪儿？","id":18,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"审判庭很快就会来这座小镇。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......什么？","id":22,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"那些邪教徒，海里的怪物，那些——","id":24,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":26,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我们......要放弃这座小镇吗？","id":27,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们？","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"不，不，孩子，只有你要离开这里，审判庭发现这里有邪教徒之后，一定会找阿戈尔人的麻烦！","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我不在乎那些邪教徒怎么样，也不在乎我们自己的命......我们在这里生活了太久，我们不知道去其他地方该怎么活下来，我们不会走。","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"但你不一样！你不是，一直想要看看外面的城市和风景吗？你还年轻，你有天赋......","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可是我、我......这太突然了。","id":38,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"这是一个机会，乔迪，一个改变的机会，最后的机会。你得勇敢一点。","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"留在这里，遭受审判庭的讯问，就算侥幸回家，也不过是在对海浪与恐鱼的担忧中空度余生。","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"可如果你离开......你的命运就握在了你自己的手里，不是那座小小的礼拜堂。","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"那座礼拜堂太小了......你不该就这么......","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"蒂亚戈叔叔......我......可是这么突然......","id":46,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"别犹豫不决了，孩子，你要坚强些，更坚强些，就像你的父母和你的祖父母辈那样。","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......我的父母，他们真的是为伊比利亚的事业奉献了生命？","id":50,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"现在说这干什么——快，来一起收拾。","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":53},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.5","id":54},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":55},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.5","id":56},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":57},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"3","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"唉，太久没见游商，都是些旧衣裳......年轻的小伙子想要穿一身新，还要费那么大力气......离开不好吗？","id":59},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可是审判庭为什么要抓阿戈尔人？如果真有邪教徒，就没可能是黎博利、菲林之类的吗？","id":61,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"阿戈尔人从海里来，怪物和灾难也从海里来。","id":63,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Dialog","id":64},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#9$1","fadetime":"0.5","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......你见过他们了？","id":67,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"不......我......等等，蒂亚戈叔叔，你知道......？你知道他们在这里？","id":69,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"嗯......我知道那些谣言不是空穴来风，我们都心知肚明。","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"胡安是他们的一员......他从小巷躲进阴暗无人的仓库，他受伤了，而且......他对我没有恶意。","id":73,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"只是因为你是个阿戈尔人，孩子。他们疯了，他们不正常，我也清楚。","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"那你为什么......难道蒂亚戈叔叔是在包庇他们？","id":77,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"这都无所谓，你很快就要离开这里了。","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"不，蒂亚戈叔叔，我不想离开。","id":81,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#13$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"什么？","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我......我生在格兰法洛，如果只是为了躲避审判庭就逃离这里，我......我不知道......","id":85,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你什么？你知道自己在说什么吗？！","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"没有阿戈尔人被带去审判庭之后还能完好无损地回来！他们要么落下残疾，要么精神失常——","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":90},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#5$1","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"——更多人直接人间蒸发了，有人说审判庭囚禁了他们，也有人说审判官直接处死了那些嫌疑犯！总之没有人回来，没有人！","id":92,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#5$1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"在那些怪物和深海教徒开始肆虐之前，“好心的”审判庭会先把这里的一切付诸一炬，没有什么比毁灭更有效的净化方法！","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#5$1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"5","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":95},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"蒂、蒂亚戈叔叔......冷静点！","id":97,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#5$1","id":98},{"type":"Text","text":"怒发冲冠的老人眼里映出乔迪的模样，就像多少年前他惴惴不安地来到这里，想要从一片废墟中亲手建起新的庭院那样。","id":99},{"type":"Text","text":"半辈子过去了，一群年轻有力的人最黄金的年纪过去了，他们在格兰法洛建立了什么？伊比利亚如今怎样？","id":100},{"type":"Text","text":"他们的添砖加瓦没有对命运产生丝毫的影响，就像投进深井的石子，而曾经他们满怀热情建起的家园如今也摇摇欲坠。","id":101},{"type":"Text","text":"巨大的虚无感吞没了蒂亚戈。如同此刻海面上的阴云，笼罩一切。","id":102},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......没有人......","id":104,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"没有人......没有人回来，马琳没有，他们都没有。格兰法洛已经在燃烧了，审判庭也好，怪物也好，我们没有出路......","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"蒂亚戈叔叔......","id":108,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......乔迪，你如果出了什么事，我没法向你的父母交代。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......我......我知道。我......","id":112,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":114,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我想去......看看海，可以吗？","id":116,"figure":"avg_4042_lumen_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":117},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"Character","id":119},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":120},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ibchurch","screenadapt":"coverall","id":121},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"寡言的教徒","text":"嘎——嘎啊啊啊啊——！","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":126},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"0.5","id":127},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.6","id":128},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":129},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"在恐惧中昏厥，你们的梦境不会好受。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"凯尔希，他们交给我。很快他们就会坦白，那些阴暗潮湿的阴谋盘踞何处。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"当然。","id":134,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"2","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Alty","text":"（哇哦，这个酷老头和你是一伙的？医生？）","id":136,"figure":"npc_2004_Alty"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你们就是......日落即逝。摇滚乐队，我不理解这些年轻人的玩意。","id":138,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Alty","text":"我希望你将其理解为音乐的神圣性。","id":140,"figure":"npc_2004_Alty"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"近几百年伊比利亚都不曾有直接目睹巨兽的记录，更妄言交流，若你们的音乐意味着你们对人类社会的看法，我倒是颇有兴趣。","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"2","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Alty","text":"《海中深色》之后，我们就没有把注意力放在这些熟悉到失去兴趣的事情上了哦。","id":144,"figure":"npc_2004_Alty"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1","name2":"npc_2004_Alty","focus":"1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"呵呵......我很好奇在你们眼中，伊比利亚是什么音色。看来漫长的生命还是可以为我带来一些惊喜。","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"那么凯尔希，如我们先前所说的那样，审判庭会尽快为你准备好前往伊比利亚之眼的手段。","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"在那之前准备好，然后尽可能扫清所有的障碍。","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2004_Alty","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Alty","text":"......那只恐鱼，对，就是现在嵌在那个怪人身体里的那个。","id":151,"figure":"npc_2004_Alty"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Alty","text":"它身上有阿戈尔人的气味。不一样的阿戈尔人，接近我们的气味，海的气味。","id":152,"figure":"npc_2004_Alty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","id":153},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"3","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......什么？","id":155,"figure":"char_003_kalts_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":156},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":158},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":159},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g18_lighthouse_square","screenadapt":"coverall","id":160},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$newhope02_intro","key":"$newhope02_loop","volume":"0.1","id":162,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":163},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.8","id":164},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":165},{"type":"Text","text":"蒂亚戈的步幅很小，但快。他显得有些衰老，但又有一股莫名的精神。","id":166},{"type":"Dialog","id":167},{"type":"MusicVolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"5","id":168},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":169},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":171},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":172},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":173},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":174},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":175},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":176},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g16_lighthouse_street","screenadapt":"coverall","id":179},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":181},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":182},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":183},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":184},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":186},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":187},{"type":"Text","text":"乔迪勉强跟随着蒂亚戈的步伐。他说，他想去看海。","id":188},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":189},{"type":"Text","text":"他不知道自己为什么要这么说。就像现在，他不确定是自己想要去，还是蒂亚戈叔叔想要去海边。","id":190},{"type":"Dialog","id":191},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":192},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g17_lighthouse_alley","screenadapt":"coverall","id":193},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":195},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":196},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":197},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":198},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":199},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":200},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":201},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":202},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4042_lumen_1#2$1","name2":"char_empty","id":203},{"type":"Text","text":"我是个阿戈尔人。乔迪想。海洋是我的家乡。","id":204},{"type":"Text","text":"可是我怎么在海里呼吸呢？那些岛民祖先，利用怎样的科技在水下生活呢？","id":205},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":206},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.3","id":207},{"type":"Text","text":"一个接一个的问题回到了青年的脑海。小的时候他就对这些问题深感好奇，可是蒂亚戈叔叔回答不了他。蒂亚戈叔叔是个黎博利。","id":208},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialog","id":210},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"可始终号称来自海洋的阿戈尔人，为什么会溺毙在海洋之中？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":213},{"type":"subtitle","id":214},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"Image","image":"27_i29","x":"100","y":"120","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":216},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"海......","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我已经记不得，上一次看见海面是什么时候了......","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"如果惩戒军还在这里，那么我们现在已经要被带走盘问了。","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"抱、抱歉，提了这样的要求......","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......没事。","id":223},{"type":"ImageTween","xTo":"20","duration":"15","block":"false","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"看看这海岸线吧......荒凉，颓废。几十年前我们曾经有个伟大的计划，这里本该是固若金汤的堡垒。","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"现在呢？东北面几公里外有一处惩戒军的哨所，西面的悬崖那头还有一座。","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"除此之外？只有一个骗局......或者是一个梦。眼前这就叫现实，提醒我们，伊比利亚一去不复返了。","id":227},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_whistle","id":228},{"type":"Text","text":"蒂亚戈吹了声口哨。乔迪很少见到蒂亚戈如此轻浮的举动。","id":229},{"type":"Text","text":"此时他似乎变换了一种身份，从一个压抑的镇长转变为了一个......工人。建设家园的工人，热血沸腾的工人。","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"啐。都过去了。我们失败了，格兰法洛是失败者的摇篮。","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你之前提到了你的父母，对吧孩子？","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......是的。","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我对海洋......没太多印象。虽然大家都说阿戈尔人，岛民，但我不明白，我生在陆地上。","id":234},{"type":"ImageTween","yTo":"40","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScale":"0.9","yScale":"0.9","duration":"30","block":"false","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"是的，你的父母，严格来说，是你的祖父母，来自阿戈尔，来自海洋的深处，那里有一个浩大的国家。","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你来自那里，孩子。","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......阿戈尔。","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"早些时候，在我们的梦想里，格兰法洛不是一座今天这样了无生机的城镇，它该是一座堡垒。一处坚固的据点。","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们会以这里为起点，修建海岸防御；我们会亲手为国家阻隔灾难，亲手让国家从灾难中复苏，亲手重建家园。","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们曾经真的是这么想的，孩子。","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":242},{"type":"Text","text":"乔迪没有出声打断。蒂亚戈的神色逐渐激动起来，某种光彩回到了这个老人混浊的眼中。","id":243},{"type":"Text","text":"他的每一寸肌肤都立了起来，他稍稍换了一个姿势，海风扬起他的眉眼，他显得高大了些。","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"而作为那个横跨半个世纪的宏伟蓝图的最后一步，我们将回到伊比利亚之眼。重启那座......灯塔。","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......灯塔？","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"灯塔，孩子。那是黄金时代的遗产，一个侥幸没有被大静谧摧毁的独孤。","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"灾难都没能摧垮我们，我们一往无前，怀揣着坚定的希望。","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"那时候......马琳戴着那顶蓝色的帽子，她说......我们都是英雄。我们都将永垂不朽。","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你的祖父母，你的父母，乔迪，格兰法洛的两代人，他们都曾为了这个蓝图努力。他们本该......永远伟大，真的。","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可是......","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"可是这里什么都不剩。","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"看见那艘船了吗，港口本来有许多的船。那本该被惩戒军带走的，他们连这都忘记了。","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"那些应有的东西什么都不剩，剩下一些垃圾，一座不起眼的小镇，数不清的麻烦，找不到出路的人，和......","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......和那艘船。","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......对。那艘船。","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我的父母，我没见过的祖父母......他们对这份职责感到骄傲吗？","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"乔迪，你不是第一次问这个问题。","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我还记得你刚懂事的时候，你刚决定留在礼拜堂做护工的时候......你都问过我。指着家里那些尘封的手册和图纸，你问过我很多次。","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我......呃，我记得。","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"是的。孩子。","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你问我几次，我都会告诉你，“是的”。无论结果如何，他们都在那场巨大的灾厄之后还保持希望，为之奉献。","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"在我们最后一次尝试前往伊比利亚之眼时，你的父母主动请缨。","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"不要责怪他们抛下年幼的你......他们承载着所有人尚未消失殆尽的信念，已经过去太多年了，我们多需要一次成功啊。","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"唉......他们带领的船队从这里离开土地，那是我们最后一次见到他们。","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"他们是英雄，孩子。马琳说，我们都该成为英雄，但现在我们都不是，只有死去的那些是了。","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......是吗。","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我的父亲母亲......","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"但是你知道，是什么毁了这一切。在那样的绝望中，我们都榨取出了所需的那丁点希望，指望点燃灯塔，结果呢？","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"是审判庭毁了这一切。审判庭抓捕了阿戈尔人，审判庭说，我们之中蛰伏着深海教会的间谍。","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"我们本该是为了伊比利亚而战的。我们却被该死的审判庭拆解得一干二净，尊严，理想，什么都不剩下。","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"孩子，你现在明白了吗？","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你该离开这里，你该远离这毫无希望的伊比利亚，想办法走远一点......去外面的国家，去更广阔的地方。","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"格兰法洛......什么都不剩下。","id":275},{"type":"Dialog","id":276},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"Image","id":279},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":280},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":281},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g17_lighthouse_alley","screenadapt":"coverall","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2002_Dan_1","fadetime":"1","id":284},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"大海！！","id":286,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"......这里完全是反方向吧。我们就把乐器丢在那么潮湿的房间里？","id":288,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"2","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"不，Aya，这里确实是海，我已经能嗅到面前浪花的味道了。","id":290,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"浪花是什么味道？","id":292,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"2","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"棉花的味道。","id":294,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"用嗅觉的词汇来表达视觉元素吗......","id":296,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"不过......你说的没错，我们的眼前确实有一片大海。","id":297,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":298},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":299},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":300},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":301},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_empty","id":302},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","fadetime":"1","id":303},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":304},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","fadetime":"1","id":305},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":306},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......你们......","id":308,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","id":309},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"阿戈尔人。而且和那些生长在陆地上的阿戈尔人截然不同。嗯......你们就是那些奇怪的阿戈尔人。","id":310,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"怎么称呼来着？喔，深海猎人。","id":311,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":312},{"type":"Character","id":313},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":314},{"type":"Text","text":"歌蕾蒂娅皱起了眉头。她极少用如此复杂的方式——皱眉头——来表露情绪。","id":315},{"type":"Text","text":"来自于深海猎人的预感，一个最出众的执政官，阿戈尔技术人员，或是战士的预感。","id":316},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你们是......日落即逝。","id":318,"figure":"char_263_skadi#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你知道她们。","id":320,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"嗯，偶然。","id":322,"figure":"char_263_skadi#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"什么呀，这么神神秘秘的......不过还是很高兴阿戈尔人也能知道我们的名字。","id":324,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"Alty她曾经因为你们留下的一些气息去过那艘舰船，大概是那会认识的吧。不过这样直接见面，还是第一次。","id":325,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"自我介绍一下吧，叫我Aya，日落即逝的主唱。这位是Dan，我们的鼓手。","id":326,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"2","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"你们好呀，海洋的来客。","id":328,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"——你们同属于海洋，很高兴认识你们。","id":330,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"抵达陆地之后，我曾在凯尔希那里学习过一些关于你们的知识——关于你们陆上同族的知识。","id":331,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"啊......你要是说陆地上的话题，那“我们”暂且还算同族，留在海里的可就说不准了。","id":333,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"你们是来做什么的？找那个医生？","id":334,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"只是按时赴约。","id":336,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我们在找回到阿戈尔的方法。","id":337,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"回阿戈尔啊......你们三个，一起？","id":339,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#4","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"1","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我们不会轻易分开。","id":341,"figure":"char_263_skadi#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","id":342},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"喔，感情真好。那后面那位呢？难道是害羞了吗，干嘛一言不发？","id":343,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1","focus":"3","id":344},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨？","text":"......","id":345},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"看得出，她不太稳定，有什么在折磨她的大脑。她病了？","id":347,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#3","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"病了，也可以这么说。","id":349,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"真可怜。","id":351,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"2","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"——唔！","id":353,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Aya","text":"怎么了，Dan？","id":355,"figure":"npc_2001_Aya_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"npc_2001_Aya_1","name2":"npc_2002_Dan_1","focus":"2","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"Dan","text":"有什么穿过了我的脊髓，就那种感觉，脑门过电，然后意识到一些自己也说不上来的——","id":357,"figure":"npc_2002_Dan_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":358},{"type":"Character","id":359},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":360},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1","fadetime":"1","id":361},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"——声音。","id":363,"figure":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":364},{"type":"Text","text":"反常沉默的幽灵鲨此刻凝视着天空。","id":365},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#3$1","id":366},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sea","loop":"true","channel":"a","volume":"0.5","id":367},{"type":"Text","text":"她闭上双眼。混沌的思绪被浪声冲刷，浪声，这里离海岸很远，但有什么正在触碰幽灵鲨的意识。","id":368},{"type":"Text","text":"它在风中，躲在云层里，越过陆地，来自海洋。","id":369},{"type":"StopSound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":370},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1","id":371},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"声音。我能听见。","id":372,"figure":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"2","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"声音......？我没有听到什么声音。","id":374,"figure":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"1","id":375},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"海的旋律，海的子嗣在哭啼。","id":376,"figure":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"那是......歌。一种歌。","id":377,"figure":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#4$1"},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"$plot_loop","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"2","id":378,"musicid":2},{"type":"Character","name":"char_263_skadi#8","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"是恐鱼的气息，越来越多，小镇遭到了袭击。","id":380,"figure":"char_263_skadi#8"},{"type":"dialog","id":381},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":382},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":384},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":385},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g18_lighthouse_square","screenadapt":"coverall","id":386},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","id":388},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":389},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":390},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"等、等等......你是......你怎么进来的？","id":392,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"你、你是审判官？！你拖着的那是——","id":393,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"回家去吧，镇民。","id":395,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"这两个人涉嫌与异教勾结，我以伊比利亚审判官的名义，履行职责。","id":396,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"离开这里，镇民们，他们的血会引来敌人，你们不应当被卷进这场战斗之中。","id":397,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"审、审判官？！审判官什么时候来到这里的——那些外人，那些外人是审判庭的眼线？","id":399,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"我、我不是邪教徒！我和那些人没有关系！","id":401,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#10$1","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你认识他们吗？","id":403,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1","id":404},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"他、他们......胡安？是胡安？我早就觉得他可疑了，他——","id":405,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":406},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"足够了。","id":407,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"不必折磨自己的内心，回家去吧，记得锁好门窗。","id":409,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1","id":410},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"慌张的镇民","text":"是、是——！","id":411,"figure":"avg_npc_460_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":412},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","id":413},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":414},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":415},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#3$1","id":416},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......","id":417,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"......来吧，别躲藏了。","id":418,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":419},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_empty","id":420},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1","id":421},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":422},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":423},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深海教徒A","text":"......嘁......审判官......不，你是大审判官之一！","id":426,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深海教徒B","text":"为什么审判庭会出现在这里？！","id":428,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":429},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深海教徒A","text":"阿玛雅和蒂亚戈都不见了，和那个阿戈尔人有关......？","id":430,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":431},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深海教徒B","text":"啧......他杀了胡安！","id":432,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":433},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"他还没死。我还需要他开口回答。","id":434,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"你们与我过去所见的敌人都不相同。你们意识清晰，你们受人指引。","id":435,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"可是，如果你们真的这么清醒而不癫狂，你们更应该明白——","id":436,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#3$1","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"——你们无法战胜我。无法战胜任何一位审判庭的勇猛战士。","id":438,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深海教徒A","text":"......啧......","id":440,"figure":"avg_npc_454_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"那你们为何还要主动献身？又为什么要飞蛾扑火？","id":442,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1","id":443},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"邪恶的浪涛许诺了你们什么？你们在这处几近废弃的海岸线盘算着什么？","id":444,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1","id":445},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"啊......我有很多问题，伊比利亚的敌人们。","id":446,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1","id":447},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"圣徒卡门","text":"但愿你们的神能替你们想出答案。","id":448,"figure":"avg_npc_447_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":449},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":451},{"type":"Character","id":452}],"characters":["蒂亚戈","乔迪","寡言的教徒","圣徒卡门","凯尔希","Alty","Dan","Aya","歌蕾蒂娅","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨？","幽灵鲨","慌张的镇民","深海教徒A","深海教徒B"]}